Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:11.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0250,,#25 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~哈哈哈哈哈~~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憎 伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格的亡灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人 亚历桑德罗·科纳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将超度你们去新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 瞄准集装箱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的话至少能炸了那对钳子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 毫发无伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点本事就像挑战Alvatore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑掉大牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 Meister们情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚…没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 机体损伤严重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与敌方两台MS交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带翼机躲在卫星附近某处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种机体状况逃不了多远的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失败了 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边去 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生死一线间都无所作为的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕吸人鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有听到世界的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括这次战斗的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额 终于有干劲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那女人瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何谓真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超兵」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中线路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合轴线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出脚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并同时攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此一时彼一时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那武器是和Throne相同的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 合体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-Armor什么的…又能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Field展开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准射击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲上去 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不悔改
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下地狱去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能  区区一台Gundam就把我的Alvatore…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我明明是完美的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不明白呢 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是什么完美的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然脑量子波带来了超快的反应能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你的思维速度却没能跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像动物一样靠本能行动而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情…才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的行动才会被看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应与思维的融合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是超兵的经典形态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续战斗 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校不在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又会孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛…玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 回答 拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是拥有原版太阳炉的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半吊子机师也能让我如此头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吗 歪曲伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格计划的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划没变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过主角变成了我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 主角就是我 亚历桑德罗·科纳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏与再生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在「天人」的武力介入下瓦解 为实现大一统而重新再生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我将以我的方式 重建这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要的是支配吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正确引导才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个新世界 容不下你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨吧 Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扼腕痛惜吧 伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统合世界 将人类带向新时代的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我这个活在当代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚的系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了世界的扭曲点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你就是其元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再生已经开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍执迷于破坏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 知道为何Exia装备有实体剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了对抗GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划中有对Gundam进行战斗的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键时刻 你将是我们最后的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一个只能选择战斗的破坏者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要战斗 为击败催生战争的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎这个世界扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用武力来根除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是「天人」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Field被…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam将成就它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚历桑德罗·科纳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是位出色的配角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并非伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是成为了我的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被统合的世界就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你竟利用了科纳一族的夙愿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 怪小气的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag 拟太阳炉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你 想死我了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为哈瓦德和达利尔 讨还血债
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这台GN Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是当时的少年？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我与你的邂逅是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 充满战斗的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为你压倒性的性能意乱情迷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉 正是所谓的爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一旦超越了爱 便因爱生恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好比过于强烈的信仰会诱发内战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然明白 为何还战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问军人为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜你所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必须击倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界如何无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是 世界的一部分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这就是世界的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了 你只不过是执迷于贯彻自我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这颗扭曲的心 由我来斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈瓦德 达利尔 血债…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没剧终
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划仍在进行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把太阳炉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive从Nadleeh上…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能安心上路 来找你了 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:16:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·比利斯…怎么会  是玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道？ 哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道的话 你就无法再战斗了 等死而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 结局都一样 我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚 难道…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔 当你读到这封信时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不在这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「以武力来根除战争」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」给了我战斗的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好比当时的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 世界如此扭曲着 这扭曲又来自何方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 人总会在无意识间产生恶意 为何 从不试图反省这份恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 会有人肆意践踏他人的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 人类支配和被支配
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何互相伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又为何 拼死挣扎求生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一直追寻着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为与你相见 就能获得答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在另一条道路上 和我有着同样的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定能找到人与人之间互相理解的道路 找到我的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直追寻着 与Gundam一同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Gundam…一同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝 好久没发邮件给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年没有收到你的回音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我有件事非说不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从今年开始将在宇宙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有过许多伤心事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我这一小小的梦想成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望帮我实现另一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着你 路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天上等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是GN粒子的光芒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里的机体？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是联邦的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子的颜色不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那光芒是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国改名为地球联邦后一年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们获得联邦全部328个成员国的赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散各国军队 实现一元化 在此宣布组建地球联邦维和军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有国家的军队都成为过去 我们维和军成为世界唯一军事组织时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的世界统一方得以成就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为先驱者 我们将全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样世界算是改变了吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢 现在的世界合您口味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人期待呢 世界的继续改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的未来从此开始 「变革者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途辛苦了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一台刚下线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正进行实战性检测
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的机体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按预定即将下线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意我参观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一代的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是0 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首台成功搭载太阳炉的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳炉已经卸下 装载在机体上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可用上它也不匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使用Exia的太阳炉 也不能保证顺利运转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界的机体  00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:40.55,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}ねえ　こんな形の出逢いしか　なかったの？　悲しいね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:52.85,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}あなたに　死んでも殺めて　欲しくも無い　お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:20:04.62,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}運命さえ飲み込まれ　沈みそうな　海へと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:14.81,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}願いよ風に乗って　夜明けの鐘を鳴らせよ　鳥のように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.58,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}my wishes over their airspace
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:27.09,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}無数の波を超え　明日へ立ち向かうあなたを　守りたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:29.79,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}my life I trade in for your pain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:35.24,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}振り向かず羽ばたけ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:42.33,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}この想いを運んで　あの空を飛んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:49.44,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}未来は誰にも　撃ち落とせない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:40.55,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}呐 除了这样的相见 别无他法么? 悲伤 彻骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:52.85,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}你 即使我堕入地狱 也不愿伤害 希望 绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:20:04.62,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}命运也被点点啃噬 堕向那绝望的深海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:14.81,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}愿望啊愿望请乘上疾风 去敲响破晓的钟 如飞鸟一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:27.09,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}超越吧超越那无数风浪 向明日抗争的你 请替我守护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:35.24,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}莫再回首 振翅去飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:42.33,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}请带着请带着这份思念 飞到那一片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:49.44,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}那是谁都不能击落的未来

